<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.9">
<l>kaṇṇālaṅ kōṭittuk kaṉṉitaṉṉaik kaippiṭippāṉ</l>
<l>tiṇṇārn tirunta cicupālaṉ tēcaḻintu</l>
<l>aṇṇān tirukkavē yāṅkavaḷaik kaippiṭitta</l>
<l>peṇṇāḷaṉ pēṇumūr pēru maraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Śrīraṅgam is the name of the town desired by the Husband of women</l>
<l>Who held Her (Rukmiṇī) hand [in marriage] there,</l>
<l>As Śiśupāla—who pictured marriage [with Rukmiṇī] in mind</l>
<l>and remained certain that he would hold the hand of the maiden [in marriage]—</l>
<l rend="indent">	lay looking upward losing lustre.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
